# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok south sudan 's ruling party signed an accord with a leading opposition party on saturday , forming an alliance ahead of a general election next april .
# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (s / sign-02
            :ARG0 (p / party
                  :ARG0-of (r / rule-03)
                  :poss (c / city
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "South"
                              :op2 "Sudan")))
            :ARG1 (a2 / accord-03
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG2 (p2 / party
                        :ARG0-of (o / oppose-01)
                        :ARG0-of (l / lead-02)))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (s2 / saturday)))
      :op2 (f / form-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (a3 / ally-01
                  :ARG1 p)
            :time (a4 / ahead
                  :op1 (e / elect-01
                        :ARG1-of (g / general-02)
                        :time (d2 / date-entity
                              :month 4
                              :mod (n2 / next))))))

                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Hamish"
                                    :op2 "Marshall"))

                  :ARG0 t

            :weekday (t2 / thursday)))
